            <p class="text-center">Sign up as a buyer or seller to get started on your real estate journey.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-2">
          <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
            <div class="rounded-circle bg-primary text-white d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mb-3" style="width: 60px; height: 60px;">
              <span class="fs-4">2</span>
